tetica y forma de la cara<\/li>\n<li>Desarrollo del habla, al perder un diente en forma prematura se altera la pronunciacion<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=&#8221;1_4&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;3.29.3&#8243; _i=&#8221;0&#8243; _address=&#8221;0.0.0&#8243;][et_pb_sidebar _builder_version=&#8221;3.29.3&#8243; area=&#8221;sidebar-2&#8243; hover_enabled=&#8221;0&#8243;][\/et_pb_sidebar][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][\/et_pb_section]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>La importancia de los dientes de leche o temporales Los dientes temporales tienen algunas diferencias con respecto a los dientes definitivos; dentro de las mas importantes podemos destacar: Esmalte mas suave y propenso al desgaste Esmalte mas fino en comparacion con el de un diente permanente Camara pulpar de mayor tama\u00f1o en proporcion a la [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_et_pb_use_builder":"on","_et_pb_old_content":"","_et_gb_content_width":"","_joinchat":[],"footnotes":""},"categories":[29],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-51750","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-salud-bucal-en-clinica-del-sur"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/clinicadelsur.cl\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/51750","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/clinicadelsur.cl\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/clinicadelsur.cl\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/clinicadelsur.cl\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/clinicadelsur.cl\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=51750"}],"version-history":[{"count":4,"href":"https:\/\/clinicadelsur.cl\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/51750\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":51792,"href":"https:\/\/clinicadelsur.cl\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/51750\/